com.mapbox.vision.safety.core

Interface VisionSafetyListener


  • public VisionSafetyListener

    Interface that user’s custom object should conform to in order to receive events from class VisionSafetyManager.

    Callbacks will not be called until Camera.calibrationProgress value reaches 1.0f due to highly imprecise results.

    NOTE: all methods are called on a background thread.

    See Also:
    class VisionSafetyManager
